title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Dec 6 2021
itunes:title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Dec 6 2021
description:
We need people in blue cities and blue states to say ENOUGH with the draconian covid measures. Is anyone really surprised about the downfall of the Cuomo bros? Reflecting on generational heroes like Band of Brothers Edward Shames and Senator Bob Dole. Dr. Marty Makary explains why he's not concerned about Omicron.
